text: Get all available one-minute options data for symbol QQQ, puts only (right=P), from 2016-01-01 through 2025-08-07. Include all contract details: bids, asks, bid sizes, ask sizes, volumes, open interest, strikes, expirations, implied volatility, greeks (delta, gamma, theta, vega), and last trade prices. Use minute-level resolution for quotes and trades data. Return data in CSV format organized by expiration dates.
